555
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:11,880
How can you say 'indulging in carnal pleasures with men'?

556
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:14,280
That's far too harsh.

557
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:16,680
Only if you fulfill your duty as the eldest son

558
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:18,600
can you inherit the family's power!

559
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:21,720
Are you afraid that the plot to rebel

560
00:41:22,520 --> 00:41:23,160
will be exposed?

561
00:41:23,240 --> 00:41:24,360
Silence!

562
00:41:25,640 --> 00:41:27,720
Do you truly wish to die?

563
00:41:29,480 --> 00:41:30,840
Kill me then.

564
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:34,680
If I die, the whole world will know

565
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:36,840
that the traitor's document bears father's name.

566
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:41,160
Do you think if this is exposed,
only I will die?

567
00:41:41,240 --> 00:41:44,040
Don't forget, thanks to whom
you enjoy your current power.

568
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:47,160
Why must I

569
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:50,520
revitalize the family and inherit power?

570
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:52,440
Because of you,

571
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:55,080
I still live in nightmares.

572
00:41:55,160 --> 00:41:57,720
You were born wild and unruly—who's to blame!

573
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:02,040
Even a stray dog knows
where it belongs.

574
00:42:02,120 --> 00:42:04,680
You wretched creature who can't tell right from wrong!

575
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:08,040
How dare you call yourself human?

576
00:42:11,240 --> 00:42:12,840
You actually favor such base things.

577
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:15,960
You

578
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:18,840
should never have been born.

579
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:38,040
My lord!

580
00:42:56,120 --> 00:42:57,000
How is his condition?

581
00:42:57,560 --> 00:42:58,920
[Doctor] It's a case of internal depression.

582
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:00,840
It's blocking the flow of qi and blood circulation.

583
00:43:00,920 --> 00:43:02,280
causing him to lose consciousness.

584
00:43:03,080 --> 00:43:06,360
I'll prescribe some Jiawei Wendan Decoction
to help calm his mind.

585
00:43:06,680 --> 00:43:08,520
Take it after each meal.

586
00:43:08,600 --> 00:43:09,720
Okay.

587
00:43:34,520 --> 00:43:36,600
Let go! Let go!

588
00:43:37,400 --> 00:43:39,240
Young master, young master!

589
00:43:39,560 --> 00:43:40,680
Young master.

590
00:43:49,640 --> 00:43:50,520
You

591
00:43:50,600 --> 00:43:52,920
should never have been born.

592
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:56,040
How could you look at your own child

593
00:43:57,080 --> 00:43:59,400
with such a cold gaze?

594
00:44:03,080 --> 00:44:05,400
He must be very lonely.

595
00:44:14,600 --> 00:44:16,680
Can you paint a picture for me?

596
00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:21,720
What flower is this?

597
00:44:22,280 --> 00:44:23,400
It's peach blossom.

598
00:44:23,960 --> 00:44:25,560
Watching the falling peach blossoms

599
00:44:25,880 --> 00:44:28,200
feels like the snow that piled up all winter
is melting.

600
00:44:28,280 --> 00:44:29,640
My heart becomes warm.

601
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:31,560
Every spring,

602
00:44:31,640 --> 00:44:33,960
I go with the sisters from the brothel
to buy Spring Festival couplets.

603
00:44:34,040 --> 00:44:37,080
When I hold the couplets and look at the peach blossoms,

604
00:44:38,360 --> 00:44:40,200
only then do I feel I truly hold spring in my hands.

605
00:44:44,840 --> 00:44:47,400
I hope you live comfortably.

606
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:57,480
Please, you can't.

607
00:44:59,240 --> 00:45:00,840
Do you like Jeong In-heon that much?

608
00:45:01,160 --> 00:45:03,000
If he passes the highest exam,

609
00:45:03,080 --> 00:45:05,160
do you think he'll take you away?

610
00:45:05,720 --> 00:45:07,320
That's impossible.

611
00:45:08,120 --> 00:45:09,120
I...

612
00:45:10,520 --> 00:45:14,040
only wish for Mr. In-heon's success in his official career.

613
00:45:17,240 --> 00:45:18,120
Sir,

614
00:45:21,800 --> 00:45:22,920
Luo Qian!

615
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:24,600
You're about to take the imperial exam, right?

616
00:45:24,920 --> 00:45:25,800
Yes.

617
00:45:27,080 --> 00:45:28,440
Did you find out anything?

618
00:45:29,720 --> 00:45:30,840
No.

619
00:45:32,840 --> 00:45:33,480
No?

620
00:45:34,760 --> 00:45:37,080
Inspector Yoon was here yesterday, I know that.

621
00:45:38,120 --> 00:45:38,760
And you say no?

622
00:45:39,560 --> 00:45:40,920
After colluding with Yoon Seung-ho,

623
00:45:41,000 --> 00:45:42,120
have you developed real feelings?

624
00:45:43,160 --> 00:45:43,800
What?

625
00:45:43,880 --> 00:45:46,200
I thought you'd do anything for me.

626
00:45:46,280 --> 00:45:47,400
Changed your mind so soon?

627
00:45:47,720 --> 00:45:48,360
Sir,

628
00:45:48,440 --> 00:45:49,560
I like you...

629
00:45:49,640 --> 00:45:50,280
Shut up!

630
00:45:51,320 --> 00:45:52,440
Since you've done such a lowly thing,

631
00:45:52,520 --> 00:45:54,120
you should at least have found out something!

632
00:46:02,600 --> 00:46:03,960
Sir will surely

633
00:46:04,280 --> 00:46:06,360
top the exam.

634
00:46:07,640 --> 00:46:09,000
Take care.

635
00:46:21,560 --> 00:46:22,440
Pour me a cup.

636
00:46:23,240 --> 00:46:24,840
This is liquor from the Qing dynasty.

637
00:46:24,920 --> 00:46:26,760
I heard Seung-ho doesn't want to see you?

638
00:46:28,520 --> 00:46:30,360
My bond with Seung-ho is extraordinary!

639
00:46:30,680 --> 00:46:32,760
While you were being turned away,

640
00:46:33,080 --> 00:46:34,680
rumors have been flying around.

641
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:35,880
I heard that lowborn became Seung-ho's lover.

642
00:46:40,760 --> 00:46:41,640
Just kill him.

643
00:46:42,920 --> 00:46:44,280
Killing a lowborn

644
00:46:45,560 --> 00:46:46,680
is a trivial matter, isn't it?

645
00:46:49,640 --> 00:46:52,200
I know him best.

646
00:46:53,960 --> 00:46:56,760
No matter what he does, I can accept it.

647
00:46:59,240 --> 00:46:59,880
Here!

648
00:47:03,320 --> 00:47:05,880
Why are you lingering by the door?

649
00:47:08,600 --> 00:47:09,240
I want to...

650
00:47:09,320 --> 00:47:10,680
Spit it out.

651
00:47:10,760 --> 00:47:11,400
So frustrating.

652
00:47:12,440 --> 00:47:15,000
I want to, before Sir In-heon leaves for Hanyang...

653
00:47:15,080 --> 00:47:18,120
I'll personally bring him a meal.

654
00:47:18,200 --> 00:47:19,320
Huh?

655
00:47:19,400 --> 00:47:21,960
Mr. Zheng left early this morning.

656
00:47:22,280 --> 00:47:23,400
Didn't he tell you?

657
00:47:29,000 --> 00:47:30,600
He did.

658
00:47:30,920 --> 00:47:32,280
I forgot!

659
00:47:36,680 --> 00:47:39,000
Since the master has left,

660
00:47:39,560 --> 00:47:41,880
I have no reason to stay here anymore.

661
00:47:44,840 --> 00:47:45,480
Luo Qian,

662
00:47:47,720 --> 00:47:49,080
Luo Qian, this painting

663
00:47:51,560 --> 00:47:52,920
was found in Mr. Zheng's room.

664
00:47:53,960 --> 00:47:54,840
It's yours, isn't it?

665
00:47:56,600 --> 00:47:57,240
Yes.

666
00:47:58,520 --> 00:47:59,880
Mr. Zheng Renxian

667
00:48:00,200 --> 00:48:01,320
left early this morning.

668
00:48:01,640 --> 00:48:04,440
Understood. You may go.

669
00:48:04,760 --> 00:48:05,400
Also...

670
00:48:12,680 --> 00:48:15,240
Someone left this letter at the door.

671
00:48:23,720 --> 00:48:26,040
Father!

672
00:48:26,360 --> 00:48:28,440
[Ten years ago]
Father, let me out...

673
00:48:28,760 --> 00:48:30,360
[Ten years ago]
Father!

674
00:48:30,440 --> 00:48:32,280
I am innocent!

675
00:48:32,840 --> 00:48:34,440
I am truly innocent!

676
00:48:35,240 --> 00:48:37,560
I did nothing wrong!

677
00:48:39,080 --> 00:48:40,680
The letter says he saw him.

678
00:48:44,600 --> 00:48:45,240
Young master,

679
00:48:45,320 --> 00:48:47,160
your body hasn't recovered yet...

680
00:49:03,320 --> 00:49:05,880
Do you think I wouldn't recognize your handwriting?

681
00:49:06,680 --> 00:49:08,520
I didn't mean to anger you with the past.

682
00:49:08,840 --> 00:49:09,720
But Seungho,

683
00:49:09,800 --> 00:49:10,920
you are the one who changed.

684
00:49:12,440 --> 00:49:13,320
I only wanted...

685
00:49:13,640 --> 00:49:14,760
to remind you of the past,

686
00:49:15,800 --> 00:49:18,120
so you would know who truly understands you!

687
00:49:20,840 --> 00:49:23,160
I can forgive all the insults you've given me,

688
00:49:23,720 --> 00:49:26,760
but I can no longer endure this pride and wait bitterly.

689
00:49:28,040 --> 00:49:29,400
I like you, Seungho.

690
00:49:30,920 --> 00:49:33,480
Don't make me more miserable.

691
00:49:38,360 --> 00:49:40,440
What do you know?

692
00:49:40,520 --> 00:49:42,600
If you truly like me,

693
00:49:43,640 --> 00:49:45,240
you shouldn't have done this.

694
00:49:49,880 --> 00:49:50,520
Father!

695
00:49:50,600 --> 00:49:51,480
We're just friends!

696
00:49:51,800 --> 00:49:52,680
You misunderstood!

697
00:50:10,520 --> 00:50:12,600
That child and his family
all died because of me.

698
00:50:12,680 --> 00:50:13,560
Because you knew

699
00:50:13,640 --> 00:50:15,240
even though I witnessed
them die before my eyes,

700
00:50:15,320 --> 00:50:17,160
if I received a letter about it,
I would surely come out to meet.

701
00:50:17,480 --> 00:50:18,600
So

702
00:50:18,680 --> 00:50:20,520
you used me.

703
00:50:22,040 --> 00:50:23,160
That's not true.

704
00:50:23,480 --> 00:50:24,840
That's not true...

705
00:50:24,920 --> 00:50:26,760
Don't harbor feelings of love for me,

706
00:50:27,800 --> 00:50:29,880
because it won't be reciprocated.

707
00:50:42,200 --> 00:50:43,560
Watch where you're going!

708
00:50:59,000 --> 00:51:01,320
I left without saying goodbye.

709
00:51:07,400 --> 00:51:08,520
That's not

710
00:51:11,000 --> 00:51:12,120
Milord,

711
00:51:14,120 --> 00:51:15,240
Milord!

712
00:51:19,160 --> 00:51:20,520
Milord, are you alright?

713
00:51:25,640 --> 00:51:27,000
He looks very ill.

714
00:51:56,600 --> 00:51:58,920
I'm afraid he's delirious with fever.

715
00:52:01,400 --> 00:52:03,480
I actually hoped that today,
the one who would say they like me

716
00:52:05,000 --> 00:52:07,080
would be you.

717
00:52:08,120 --> 00:52:11,160
The day you mistook me for Jeong In-heon
and fell into my arms,

718
00:52:12,920 --> 00:52:15,000
the way you confessed you loved me,

719
00:52:17,240 --> 00:52:19,320
why does it keep lingering
in my mind?

720
00:52:21,320 --> 00:52:24,120
Jihwa said I made him miserable.

721
00:52:25,640 --> 00:52:27,000
Now it's my turn.

722
00:52:29,960 --> 00:52:32,040
You've made me restless.

723
00:52:34,520 --> 00:52:35,880
Don't go.

724
00:52:41,960 --> 00:52:43,320
Impossible.

725
00:52:46,280 --> 00:52:50,040
Milord actually likes me?

726
00:53:07,880 --> 00:53:09,000
[Deokjae] Milord, you've arrived.

727
00:53:27,800 --> 00:53:28,920
Is he dead?

728
00:53:29,720 --> 00:53:30,600
Should I kill him?

729
00:53:30,920 --> 00:53:32,280
No one saw it,
no one heard it.

730
00:53:32,600 --> 00:53:33,480
Everyone will think

731
00:53:33,560 --> 00:53:34,920
he ran away.

732
00:53:42,440 --> 00:53:44,760
We can cut off his head
so no one recognizes him.

733
00:53:44,840 --> 00:53:46,680
We can also gouge out his eyes
and cut out his tongue.

734
00:53:47,000 --> 00:53:48,360
Throw him into the mountains.

735
00:53:49,160 --> 00:53:50,520
So he can never be a spring painter again.

736
00:53:56,120 --> 00:53:57,960
The rumors are rampant.

737
00:53:58,040 --> 00:53:59,400
I heard that commoner
became Seungho's lover.

738
00:54:00,200 --> 00:54:00,840
Just kill him directly.

739
00:54:04,760 --> 00:54:08,520
If only he disappears...

740
00:54:10,280 --> 00:54:11,880
Don't harbor feelings of love for me.

741
00:54:13,160 --> 00:54:15,000
Because there will be no return.

742
00:54:17,480 --> 00:54:18,600
If he dies...

743
00:54:19,640 --> 00:54:21,480
Will Yoon Seungho come back to me?

744
00:54:26,120 --> 00:54:28,200
If you truly like me,

745
00:54:29,480 --> 00:54:30,840
you shouldn't do this.

746
00:54:33,320 --> 00:54:34,680
It's all ruined by me...

747
00:54:36,440 --> 00:54:38,520
Even without him,
Yoon Seungho won't come back to me!

748
00:54:49,880 --> 00:54:50,520
Where is the person?

749
00:54:51,560 --> 00:54:52,440
I let him go.

750
00:54:53,480 --> 00:54:54,120
What?

751
00:54:55,160 --> 00:54:56,280
Just kill him to silence him.

752
00:54:56,360 --> 00:54:57,720
Why make things so complicated!

753
00:54:59,960 --> 00:55:00,840
If Yoon Seungho finds out,

754
00:55:00,920 --> 00:55:02,520
do you think he'll let us off?

755
00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:05,640
Young master,

756
00:55:07,640 --> 00:55:09,720
Before abandoning him, I warned him
not to speak of it.

757
00:55:10,760 --> 00:55:11,880
Is there anything else you need?

758
00:55:19,640 --> 00:55:20,760
What are you doing!

759
00:55:22,040 --> 00:55:23,640
He knows it was us.

760
00:55:24,920 --> 00:55:26,280
A family that can betray even its master

761
00:55:27,560 --> 00:55:28,440
must be killed.

762
00:55:41,960 --> 00:55:42,840
Na-gyeom...

763
00:55:44,600 --> 00:55:45,720
Is Luo Qian here?

764
00:55:50,600 --> 00:55:51,480
Yes, young master!

765
00:55:58,040 --> 00:55:59,400
Young master, are you feeling better?

766
00:56:03,560 --> 00:56:04,920
Where is Luo Qian?

767
00:56:10,520 --> 00:56:11,640
Seems like he left...

768
00:56:19,160 --> 00:56:21,240
And I poured out my heart like that...

769
00:56:25,880 --> 00:56:27,720
Go find Luo Qian and bring him back!

770
00:56:38,360 --> 00:56:40,920
If Yoon Seong-ho finds out about today,
you're dead for sure.

771
00:56:48,920 --> 00:56:51,000
Lord Seong-ho...

772
00:56:51,800 --> 00:56:53,400
I miss you so much.

773
00:56:59,240 --> 00:57:00,360
[Sina] Luo Qian!

774
00:57:03,560 --> 00:57:04,200
Luo Qian

775
00:57:06,200 --> 00:57:08,520
I heard Luo Qian is at the brothel.

776
00:57:14,600 --> 00:57:15,240
Luo Qian!

777
00:57:22,760 --> 00:57:23,880
Where is Luo Qian!

778
00:57:26,840 --> 00:57:27,480
What are you doing!

779
00:57:27,800 --> 00:57:28,759
Move aside!

780
00:57:28,760 --> 00:57:29,640
Luo Qian!

781
00:57:39,800 --> 00:57:40,920
Luo Qian, get up!

782
00:57:44,360 --> 00:57:45,000
My lord?

783
00:57:55,160 --> 00:57:57,720
I didn't expect you to leave so quickly.

784
00:58:01,880 --> 00:58:03,480
Scared off by my confession
and fled overnight?

785
00:58:05,240 --> 00:58:07,320
I didn't flee...

786
00:58:10,040 --> 00:58:13,080
If not fleeing, then what? Tell me!

787
00:58:18,200 --> 00:58:19,560
I can't say.

788
00:58:28,280 --> 00:58:30,360
Finally rid of me, happy?

789
00:58:32,120 --> 00:58:33,480
I was wrong.

790
00:58:36,920 --> 00:58:37,800
Seong-ho

791
00:58:38,120 --> 00:58:39,000
Are you in there?

792
00:58:50,600 --> 00:58:51,480
What is it?

793
00:58:52,280 --> 00:58:53,640
Is Luo Qian locked inside?

794
00:58:54,680 --> 00:58:55,800
If nothing, get lost.

795
00:58:57,080 --> 00:58:58,200
This Luo Qian

796
00:58:58,760 --> 00:58:59,880
didn't flee at all.

797
00:59:01,400 --> 00:59:02,280
What?

798
00:59:03,800 --> 00:59:05,400
Looks like Ji-hwa did it.

799
00:59:06,440 --> 00:59:07,800
He said he would kidnap Luo Qian.

800
00:59:08,120 --> 00:59:09,240
I thought he was just talking.

801
00:59:10,520 --> 00:59:11,880
Didn't expect he actually had the guts.

802
00:59:13,160 --> 00:59:14,520
Don't be too angry.

803
00:59:14,840 --> 00:59:17,400
At least he came back with all limbs intact.

804
00:59:19,640 --> 00:59:21,240
You...

805
00:59:21,320 --> 00:59:22,920
Why did you tell me this?

806
00:59:27,560 --> 00:59:29,160
Lord Seungho...

807
00:59:30,440 --> 00:59:31,800
I'm so scared...

808
00:59:33,800 --> 00:59:34,800
My lord...

809
00:59:37,640 --> 00:59:39,720
We can cut off his head
so no one recognizes him.

810
00:59:40,760 --> 00:59:42,360
Or gouge out his eyes
and cut out his tongue.

811
00:59:42,920 --> 00:59:44,280
Throw him into the mountains.

812
00:59:44,840 --> 00:59:46,440
So he can never be a erotic painting artist again.

813
01:00:05,960 --> 01:00:07,320
I was wrong...

814
01:00:07,640 --> 01:00:09,960
It was my fault.

815
01:00:10,040 --> 01:00:12,120
Please spare me.

816
01:00:25,880 --> 01:00:27,000
Lee Jihwa, come out!

817
01:00:51,080 --> 01:00:53,400
If you dare touch Nakyum again...

818
01:00:54,440 --> 01:00:55,080
No.

819
01:00:55,880 --> 01:00:57,960
If you shamelessly
show your face before me again,

820
01:00:59,000 --> 01:01:00,360
I will definitely kill you.

821
01:01:07,160 --> 01:01:08,280
You can still laugh?

822
01:01:08,600 --> 01:01:10,440
Yoon Seungho wants to kill me.

823
01:01:11,480 --> 01:01:13,560
Sorry.

824
01:01:18,200 --> 01:01:20,280
How did Yoon Seungho find out?

825
01:01:20,360 --> 01:01:22,440
I killed that servant with my own hands.

826
01:01:23,240 --> 01:01:23,880
Then

827
01:01:25,160 --> 01:01:26,520
who else could it be?

828
01:01:27,560 --> 01:01:28,680
Nakyum?

829
01:01:28,760 --> 01:01:29,760
That's why

830
01:01:29,960 --> 01:01:31,560
I told you to act more decisively.

831
01:01:33,320 --> 01:01:34,680
Help me.

832
01:01:35,000 --> 01:01:36,600
Yoon Seungho will kill me.

833
01:01:36,920 --> 01:01:37,800
I

834
01:01:39,320 --> 01:01:40,440
