1111
01:23:09,080 --> 01:23:09,720
My lord

1112
01:23:10,520 --> 01:23:11,400
What's wrong?

1113
01:23:11,960 --> 01:23:13,800
I

1114
01:23:15,080 --> 01:23:18,120
did not believe

1115
01:23:18,200 --> 01:23:20,520
that you killed Mr. In-heon.

1116
01:23:20,840 --> 01:23:22,680
You ran out of the brothel immediately.

1117
01:23:23,000 --> 01:23:24,360
And you expect me to trust you?

1118
01:23:24,680 --> 01:23:26,760
I thought it was impossible...

1119
01:23:29,960 --> 01:23:32,040
But what if it's true?

1120
01:23:33,080 --> 01:23:35,400
I wanted to ask quickly.

1121
01:23:36,440 --> 01:23:37,320
So I've been

1122
01:23:38,360 --> 01:23:40,200
waiting for you to come.

1123
01:23:44,120 --> 01:23:45,120
Heung

1124
01:23:47,480 --> 01:23:49,320
Don't try to recall that day.

1125
01:23:50,120 --> 01:23:52,920
Mr. In-heon
was trapped for a few days

1126
01:23:53,240 --> 01:23:55,080
on his way back from the civil service exam.

1127
01:23:55,400 --> 01:23:57,720
You're just worried about him.

1128
01:23:58,520 --> 01:23:59,880
It was just a nightmare.

1129
01:24:02,120 --> 01:24:03,960
Please give me another chance.

1130
01:24:04,280 --> 01:24:07,080
Can't even handle this small task I assigned.

1131
01:24:07,400 --> 01:24:09,000
And you still dream of becoming the top scholar...

1132
01:24:09,800 --> 01:24:10,920
The deal between us

1133
01:24:11,000 --> 01:24:12,120
Consider it never happened.

1134
01:24:13,160 --> 01:24:14,040
Please trust me!

1135
01:24:15,080 --> 01:24:16,680
As long as I can appease that Luo Qian guy,

1136
01:24:17,000 --> 01:24:19,080
I will definitely find the Tongwen!

1137
01:24:21,800 --> 01:24:23,880
Do you know why I asked you to handle this?

1138
01:24:24,680 --> 01:24:25,800
Me?

1139
01:24:26,840 --> 01:24:29,400
I like people who have nothing.

1140
01:24:30,440 --> 01:24:32,760
Because they will stop at nothing

1141
01:24:32,840 --> 01:24:35,160
for fame and fortune.

1142
01:24:36,920 --> 01:24:38,040
I will definitely

1143
01:24:38,840 --> 01:24:40,440
bring the Tongwen.

1144
01:24:42,440 --> 01:24:44,280
Don't disappoint me.

1145
01:24:47,480 --> 01:24:48,840
A fire?

1146
01:24:48,920 --> 01:24:49,639
The authorities

1147
01:24:49,640 --> 01:24:51,480
said the young masters were smoking opium,

1148
01:24:51,560 --> 01:24:53,880
which caused the fire to spread, and closed the case.

1149
01:24:54,440 --> 01:24:55,560
It seems the master

1150
01:24:55,640 --> 01:24:57,000
has settled the matter.

1151
01:24:57,800 --> 01:24:58,920
What about Zheng Renxian?

1152
01:24:59,000 --> 01:25:00,600
I heard he came first in the imperial exam.

1153
01:25:04,040 --> 01:25:05,880
I think I need to leave here.

1154
01:25:06,680 --> 01:25:07,320
What did you say?

1155
01:25:07,640 --> 01:25:09,000
Send a letter to the brothel,

1156
01:25:09,560 --> 01:25:11,640
saying Luo Qian will return to the establishment.

1157
01:25:12,680 --> 01:25:13,800
Yes, understood.

1158
01:25:21,800 --> 01:25:22,800
I want this pair.

1159
01:25:24,920 --> 01:25:25,800
Sir,

1160
01:25:25,880 --> 01:25:27,240
I don't need new shoes...

1161
01:25:46,280 --> 01:25:48,600
Make it with this cloth.
[Merchant] Yes, sir.

1162
01:26:02,600 --> 01:26:03,960
I'll take all the pens here.

1163
01:26:05,240 --> 01:26:05,880
What?

1164
01:26:06,920 --> 01:26:08,280
All of them?

1165
01:26:17,720 --> 01:26:19,080
Why am I so uneasy?

1166
01:26:26,600 --> 01:26:27,480
My lord!

1167
01:26:40,280 --> 01:26:41,880
It suits you perfectly!

1168
01:26:53,720 --> 01:26:55,320
How do I look?

1169
01:26:56,360 --> 01:26:57,480
Beautiful.

1170
01:27:02,360 --> 01:27:22,200
The new top scholar has arrived!

1171
01:27:25,400 --> 01:27:27,480
Seeing Jeong In-heon achieve success and fame

1172
01:27:27,800 --> 01:27:28,680
makes you that happy?

1173
01:27:31,400 --> 01:27:33,240
I have always envisioned

1174
01:27:33,320 --> 01:27:35,880
you wearing the scholar's flower

1175
01:27:35,960 --> 01:27:37,080
as you go out.

1176
01:27:38,120 --> 01:27:39,960
Not only did I imagine it in my mind,

1177
01:27:40,760 --> 01:27:42,120
I also drew it on paper.

1178
01:27:43,400 --> 01:27:44,280
In that painting,

1179
01:27:45,800 --> 01:27:46,920
were you there?

1180
01:27:48,440 --> 01:27:50,040
I dared not approach,

1181
01:27:51,320 --> 01:27:52,920
so I could only watch from afar.

1182
01:27:56,600 --> 01:27:59,400
Do you know the biggest difference between now and that painting?

1183
01:28:04,760 --> 01:28:06,360
It's that you are by my side.

1184
01:28:20,120 --> 01:28:20,760
My lord,

1185
01:28:22,040 --> 01:28:23,880
have you ever eaten grilled rice cakes?

1186
01:28:25,640 --> 01:28:26,520
You haven't, have you?

1187
01:28:27,080 --> 01:28:28,200
I'll grill some for you!

1188
01:28:29,240 --> 01:28:29,880
When I was little,

1189
01:28:30,200 --> 01:28:31,800
Whenever I cried, Sister Xina would

1190
01:28:38,840 --> 01:28:42,120
Why are you looking at me like that?

1191
01:28:47,240 --> 01:28:48,360
I feel so uneasy.

1192
01:28:54,200 --> 01:28:56,040
- About two plates.
- Two plates?

1193
01:28:56,360 --> 01:28:58,200
- Isn't that too much?
- Too much.

1194
01:28:59,240 --> 01:29:01,560
Sir, thank you for saving Luo Qian.

1195
01:29:03,560 --> 01:29:04,680
You're right.

1196
01:29:08,120 --> 01:29:09,000
What?

1197
01:29:09,080 --> 01:29:11,880
Luo Qian staying with me
will only bring him misfortune.

1198
01:29:12,200 --> 01:29:14,280
Although he's still in pain from that day,

1199
01:29:15,080 --> 01:29:17,160
he tries hard to hide it in front of me.

1200
01:29:20,120 --> 01:29:22,200
I only make him sad and hurt.

1201
01:29:23,240 --> 01:29:25,320
You treat him like a sister.
I hope you can take care of him.

1202
01:29:27,080 --> 01:29:28,440
I entrust Luo Qian to you.

1203
01:29:30,920 --> 01:29:32,280
Luo Qian,

1204
01:29:34,760 --> 01:29:36,600
really likes you.

1205
01:29:38,120 --> 01:29:39,000
No matter what happens in the future,

1206
01:29:41,000 --> 01:29:43,320
please come back to find him.

1207
01:29:51,800 --> 01:29:53,400
Why hasn't the lord come yet?

1208
01:29:58,520 --> 01:29:59,640
Sister Xina!

1209
01:30:02,840 --> 01:30:03,480
Where is the lord?

1210
01:30:06,920 --> 01:30:07,800
What's wrong?

1211
01:30:08,840 --> 01:30:09,720
Luo Qian,

1212
01:30:11,720 --> 01:30:13,560
from now on, live with me.

1213
01:30:16,520 --> 01:30:19,080
Lord Seongho has left.

1214
01:30:26,840 --> 01:30:27,840
Lord...

1215
01:30:30,680 --> 01:30:44,760
Lord!

1216
01:30:45,800 --> 01:30:46,920
Wait for me!

1217
01:30:55,160 --> 01:30:57,240
Your body hasn't recovered yet.
Why aren't you more careful?

1218
01:30:57,320 --> 01:30:58,200
Lord!

1219
01:30:59,240 --> 01:31:00,840
You forgot to take me with you.

1220
01:31:02,120 --> 01:31:03,000
Luo Qian,

1221
01:31:03,080 --> 01:31:04,440
let's go home quickly.

1222
01:31:05,720 --> 01:31:07,320
I'm already better.

1223
01:31:09,080 --> 01:31:10,920
Why did you send me away?

1224
01:31:11,720 --> 01:31:13,320
When I wanted to leave you,

1225
01:31:13,400 --> 01:31:15,000
you refused to let me go no matter what.

1226
01:31:15,080 --> 01:31:18,120
I

1227
01:31:21,320 --> 01:31:22,920
Did I do something wrong?

1228
01:31:29,960 --> 01:31:34,200
Don't you like me anymore?

1229
01:31:44,120 --> 01:31:45,240
Luo Qian,

1230
01:31:47,000 --> 01:31:48,600
I will definitely solve everything
and come back for you.

1231
01:31:49,640 --> 01:31:50,640
For now,

1232
01:31:51,560 --> 01:31:52,680
stay here for now.

1233
01:31:54,440 --> 01:31:55,080
Sir...

1234
01:32:26,840 --> 01:32:28,920
What did you trade for this top scholar title?

1235
01:32:29,720 --> 01:32:31,320
Could it be that you sold yourself?

1236
01:32:31,400 --> 01:32:32,520
What?

1237
01:32:35,240 --> 01:32:36,840
Do you really want to kill me?

1238
01:32:36,920 --> 01:32:38,760
Killing four noble young masters was nothing,

1239
01:32:39,080 --> 01:32:41,160
killing one more commoner like you
would be a piece of cake.

1240
01:32:41,240 --> 01:32:42,360
It was three.

1241
01:32:42,440 --> 01:32:43,080
What did you say?

1242
01:32:43,400 --> 01:32:45,240
Young Master Min is not dead yet.

1243
01:32:45,800 --> 01:32:48,840
Ah, but don't worry,

1244
01:32:48,920 --> 01:32:50,040
I've already taken care of him.

1245
01:32:55,160 --> 01:32:57,000
If you kill me with your own hands,

1246
01:32:59,480 --> 01:33:01,800
Luo Qian will be very sad.

1247
01:33:06,200 --> 01:33:07,320
Tell my father,

1248
01:33:08,600 --> 01:33:11,160
if he dares to touch him again,
the entire Yin family will die.

1249
01:33:11,480 --> 01:33:13,080
If you don't want to end up dead together,

1250
01:33:14,120 --> 01:33:15,480
then behave yourself.

1251
01:33:21,560 --> 01:33:24,120
If Yin Shenghao makes the announcement public,

1252
01:33:24,200 --> 01:33:27,480
I will end up with nothing.

1253
01:33:27,560 --> 01:33:30,120
It must be handed over to Lord Yin by me personally.

1254
01:33:41,240 --> 01:33:42,840
Sir?

1255
01:33:46,280 --> 01:33:47,400
Luo Qian,

1256
01:33:48,440 --> 01:33:49,560
are you feeling okay?

1257
01:33:50,360 --> 01:33:51,240
I heard that while I was away,

1258
01:33:51,560 --> 01:33:53,880
you almost met with misfortune...

1259
01:33:55,400 --> 01:33:57,000
Yes, sir...

1260
01:33:57,080 --> 01:33:58,680
When I heard the news,

1261
01:33:58,760 --> 01:34:00,600
my heart shattered.

1262
01:34:01,400 --> 01:34:02,760
You must have been so scared...

1263
01:34:04,520 --> 01:34:06,600
I should stay by your side...

1264
01:34:17,000 --> 01:34:18,360
Now I understand

1265
01:34:19,640 --> 01:34:21,000
My feelings for you

1266
01:34:21,080 --> 01:34:23,400
Have gone beyond that of master and disciple...

1267
01:34:24,440 --> 01:34:25,800
Come with me

1268
01:34:27,800 --> 01:34:28,440
I know

1269
01:34:28,520 --> 01:34:30,360
You're worried that if you leave,

1270
01:34:30,440 --> 01:34:31,560
Yoon Seung-ho won't let it go

1271
01:34:32,600 --> 01:34:34,920
Yoon Seung-ho almost killed me too

1272
01:34:40,520 --> 01:34:41,880
If we're to leave together,

1273
01:34:42,200 --> 01:34:44,040
There's something you need to do

1274
01:34:45,080 --> 01:34:46,680
Yoon Seung-ho has a document

1275
01:34:47,480 --> 01:34:49,080
Only if you bring it
can we leave together...

1276
01:34:49,400 --> 01:34:51,720
Master, you don't like me

1277
01:34:53,480 --> 01:34:54,120
What?

1278
01:34:55,160 --> 01:34:58,200
Now I understand
what the gaze of someone in love

1279
01:34:59,720 --> 01:35:00,840
looks like

1280
01:35:03,800 --> 01:35:05,400
You make me restless

1281
01:35:06,920 --> 01:35:10,680
Master has never looked at me
with such eyes

1282
01:35:11,000 --> 01:35:12,600
I said I love you

1283
01:35:12,680 --> 01:35:14,760
I want to be with Lord Seung-ho

1284
01:35:17,480 --> 01:35:19,800
You would betray me for Yoon Seung-ho?

1285
01:35:21,560 --> 01:35:23,400
You say Yoon Seung-ho likes you too?

1286
01:35:23,480 --> 01:35:25,560
You're flattering yourself

1287
01:35:25,880 --> 01:35:28,440
Do you really believe that shameless man
will stay with you for life?

1288
01:35:28,520 --> 01:35:30,840
Once he gets bored,
he'll abandon you immediately

1289
01:35:30,920 --> 01:35:32,520
And throw yourself into another man's arms!

1290
01:35:34,760 --> 01:35:36,840
Lord Seung-ho is not that kind of person

1291
01:35:42,200 --> 01:35:43,200
One—

1292
01:35:47,000 --> 01:35:47,880
My lord!

1293
01:35:47,960 --> 01:35:51,480
With this kid Baek Na-gyeon,
we can get the document!

1294
01:35:52,520 --> 01:35:54,120
Please trust me one more time!

1295
01:35:54,200 --> 01:35:57,000
Just threaten Yoon Seung-ho
that you'll kill this kid,

1296
01:35:57,320 --> 01:35:58,680
and he will surely hand over the document!

1297
01:35:59,000 --> 01:35:59,640
My lord!

1298
01:36:07,880 --> 01:36:08,520
My lord,

1299
01:36:09,800 --> 01:36:12,120
Is this servant enough?

1300
01:36:12,200 --> 01:36:12,840
Yes!

1301
01:36:14,120 --> 01:36:15,480
I'll take care of it!

1302
01:36:16,040 --> 01:36:17,640
Please trust me one more time!

1303
01:36:18,680 --> 01:36:21,000
This kid will help me get the document.

1304
01:36:22,520 --> 01:36:23,160
Then you,

1305
01:36:24,200 --> 01:36:25,800
what can you get for me?

1306
01:36:27,080 --> 01:36:27,720
What did you say?

1307
01:36:30,920 --> 01:36:32,040
Kill him.

1308
01:36:34,760 --> 01:36:35,400
My lord!

1309
01:36:36,440 --> 01:36:37,800
My lord, you can't do this!

1310
01:36:38,360 --> 01:36:39,240
-My lord!
-[Eunuch Yi's servant] Go!

1311
01:36:39,800 --> 01:36:40,440
Let go of me, you bastard!

1312
01:36:41,000 --> 01:36:43,080
My lord! I beg you to spare my life!

1313
01:36:43,160 --> 01:36:44,040
Luo Qian, wake up!

1314
01:36:44,360 --> 01:36:45,360
Luo Qian!

1315
01:36:59,240 --> 01:37:00,600
Luo... Qian...

1316
01:37:11,960 --> 01:37:19,080
Luo Qian

1317
01:37:19,880 --> 01:37:21,720
Why keep calling me, my lord...

1318
01:37:23,000 --> 01:37:24,360
I just really want to say your name.

1319
01:37:28,040 --> 01:37:28,920
Lord Shenghao.

1320
01:37:31,160 --> 01:37:32,280
It sounds so nice.

1321
01:37:33,800 --> 01:37:34,920
Say it again.

1322
01:37:36,680 --> 01:37:37,560
Ah, my lord!

1323
01:37:53,000 --> 01:37:55,800
You turned my son into a murderer!

1324
01:37:55,880 --> 01:37:56,520
What?

1325
01:37:57,560 --> 01:38:00,600
He killed four young masters in the cabin outside the South Gate.

1326
01:38:00,680 --> 01:38:02,280
It's all because of you!

1327
01:38:03,320 --> 01:38:04,200
Because of you,

1328
01:38:04,520 --> 01:38:06,840
my son is waiting to die in the government office!

1329
01:38:06,920 --> 01:38:09,480
Lord Shenghao is going to be executed?

1330
01:38:09,560 --> 01:38:10,440
That's right.

1331
01:38:11,480 --> 01:38:12,120
No!

1332
01:38:14,600 --> 01:38:15,960
My lord,

1333
01:38:16,280 --> 01:38:17,880
please save Lord Shenghao.

1334
01:38:18,200 --> 01:38:21,240
It's all because of me; my lord has no fault at all.

1335
01:38:26,120 --> 01:38:26,760
Shenghao,

1336
01:38:28,520 --> 01:38:29,640
No fault at all?

1337
01:38:30,440 --> 01:38:31,440
Yes.

1338
01:38:31,880 --> 01:38:33,000
It's all because of me.

1339
01:38:34,040 --> 01:38:35,640
It's all because I'm useless, being pushed around like trash...

1340
01:38:37,400 --> 01:38:38,040
Yes.

1341
01:38:39,320 --> 01:38:40,200
So it was you

1342
01:38:41,240 --> 01:38:42,360
who killed the young masters

1343
01:38:43,400 --> 01:38:44,520
and set the fire, right?

1344
01:38:47,240 --> 01:38:48,240
What?

1345
01:38:49,640 --> 01:38:52,200
Because you couldn't bear the nobles' humiliation

1346
01:38:53,720 --> 01:38:54,840
you caused this disaster

1347
01:38:56,360 --> 01:38:57,000
Is that it?

1348
01:39:02,840 --> 01:39:05,880
Yes... yes

1349
01:39:05,960 --> 01:39:07,560
I killed them!

1350
01:39:11,480 --> 01:39:12,360
As the young master ordered,

1351
01:39:13,400 --> 01:39:14,760
I found a house in a secluded place far from Hanyang.

1352
01:39:14,840 --> 01:39:15,960
Would you like to see it?

1353
01:39:16,760 --> 01:39:17,640
No need.

1354
01:39:18,920 --> 01:39:19,560
Prepare and go directly.

1355
01:39:20,360 --> 01:39:21,960
I need to pack all the belongings; it will take some time.

1356
01:39:22,040 --> 01:39:24,600
Take Luo Qian with you first.

1357
01:39:25,880 --> 01:39:28,200
I have matters to attend to.

1358
01:39:28,520 --> 01:39:30,120
Lord Seong-ho!

1359
01:39:30,440 --> 01:39:32,760
Luo Qian

1360
01:39:36,920 --> 01:39:38,040
has confessed to killing the young masters.

1361
01:39:38,120 --> 01:39:40,680
What?

1362
01:39:42,920 --> 01:39:43,920
Step back!

1363
01:39:47,720 --> 01:39:48,600
Move aside!

1364
01:39:48,680 --> 01:39:49,320
Luo Qian!

1365
01:39:50,120 --> 01:39:52,200
Stop!

1366
01:39:52,520 --> 01:39:53,520
Come in.

1367
01:39:54,200 --> 01:39:55,320
Lord Yoon orders you to enter.

1368
01:39:55,400 --> 01:39:57,480
Luo Qian!

1369
01:39:59,960 --> 01:40:00,600
My lord?

1370
01:40:04,760 --> 01:40:05,760
Luo Qian,

1371
01:40:09,560 --> 01:40:10,200
you cannot stay here.

1372
01:40:12,440 --> 01:40:13,080
Leave quickly.

1373
01:40:13,400 --> 01:40:14,280
Luo Qian,

1374
01:40:15,800 --> 01:40:16,279
If you stay, you'll be suspected too.

1375
01:40:16,280 --> 01:40:18,120
I can't let you take the blame for me.

1376
01:40:19,160 --> 01:40:21,480
Let's go together.

1377
01:40:22,760 --> 01:40:23,400
No.

1378
01:40:27,560 --> 01:40:28,920
I killed him.

1379
01:40:30,920 --> 01:40:31,560
Luo Qian.

1380
01:40:33,560 --> 01:40:34,440
I've lived until now

1381
01:40:35,720 --> 01:40:37,080
never once thought

1382
01:40:38,120 --> 01:40:39,480
about what kind of life I wanted.

1383
01:40:41,960 --> 01:40:43,560
Since meeting you, I've started to look forward to tomorrow,

1384
01:40:45,080 --> 01:40:47,160
look forward to the arrival of the next season.

1385
01:40:52,040 --> 01:40:53,640
I can't live without you...

1386
01:41:17,240 --> 01:41:18,120
I

1387
01:41:20,840 --> 01:41:22,200
will definitely save you.

1388
01:41:33,800 --> 01:41:35,400
[Establish the 'Great Alliance Pact' to promote learning]

1389
01:41:35,480 --> 01:41:37,800
[A document recording the names of those plotting rebellion]

1390
01:41:38,840 --> 01:41:41,160
[Yi Changxian]

1391
01:41:56,840 --> 01:41:58,200
Please release Luo Qian.

1392
01:42:01,640 --> 01:42:04,200
You've already gotten what you wanted. Stop while you're ahead.

1393
01:42:05,000 --> 01:42:06,360
Do you think this document alone

1394
01:42:06,440 --> 01:42:09,000
can save your lover?

1395
01:42:20,120 --> 01:42:22,440
From now on, I will follow your orders.

1396
01:42:22,760 --> 01:42:24,840
Why should I trust you?

1397
01:42:25,160 --> 01:42:27,960
I will be the upright son you wish me to be,

1398
01:42:28,760 --> 01:42:31,800
and do my utmost to cleanse our family's shame.

1399
01:42:32,600 --> 01:42:34,680
I beg you, Father, to save his life.

1400
01:42:34,760 --> 01:42:36,360
You may exploit my weaknesses,

1401
01:42:37,160 --> 01:42:39,000
manipulate me as you please.

1402
01:42:41,960 --> 01:42:43,560
I bow my head and plead.

1403
01:42:51,080 --> 01:42:52,080
Come out.

1404
01:42:52,280 --> 01:42:53,160
What?

1405
01:42:55,400 --> 01:42:56,280
Have you heard?

1406
01:42:56,600 --> 01:42:58,680
It's about the massacre in the wooden house outside the South Gate!

1407
01:42:59,000 --> 01:43:00,600
The culprit is actually the scholar Jeong In-heon!

1408
01:43:00,680 --> 01:43:02,040
That's right!

1409
01:43:02,360 --> 01:43:04,200
It must be that erotic painting artist who stepped forward to take the blame

1410
01:43:04,280 --> 01:43:06,120
to protect this scholar!

1411
01:43:07,400 --> 01:43:09,000
I heard that in the mountains over there,

1412
01:43:09,080 --> 01:43:11,640
a body gnawed by wild animals was found.

1413
01:43:13,160 --> 01:43:15,720
Rumor has it that it's Jeong In-heon. Is that true?

1414
01:43:15,800 --> 01:43:17,160
Let me go!

1415
01:43:17,720 --> 01:43:19,080
I killed them all.

1416
01:43:19,640 --> 01:43:20,760
I killed every single one!

1417
01:43:23,000 --> 01:43:23,640
Go now!

1418
01:43:41,240 --> 01:43:41,880
Luo Qian

1419
01:43:43,880 --> 01:43:45,240
Let's run away together.

1420
01:43:47,240 --> 01:43:49,320
Only this way
can we help Lord Shenghao.

1421
01:43:54,440 --> 01:43:55,560
[Three years later]

1422
01:43:55,880 --> 01:43:57,240
Well drawn.

1423
01:43:59,480 --> 01:44:00,199
[Country kid 1] Brother!

1424
01:44:00,200 --> 01:44:01,320
I finished drawing!

1425
01:44:01,640 --> 01:44:02,280
[Country kid 2] I finished too!

1426
01:44:02,600 --> 01:44:03,960
Let me see.

1427
01:44:04,760 --> 01:44:06,120
Well drawn.

1428
01:44:08,120 --> 01:44:09,000
What is this?

1429
01:44:09,800 --> 01:44:10,440
A quilt!

1430
01:44:10,760 --> 01:44:11,640
A quilt?

1431
01:44:11,960 --> 01:44:12,600
Mom and Dad

1432
01:44:12,920 --> 01:44:15,000
are inside.

1433
01:44:20,120 --> 01:44:22,200
May disasters vanish like spring snow,
and blessings rise like summer clouds.

1434
01:44:24,200 --> 01:44:24,840
Luo Qian!

1435
01:44:28,520 --> 01:44:29,520
Sister!

1436
01:44:32,360 --> 01:44:33,720
Ouch.

1437
01:44:35,480 --> 01:44:36,360
Are all the sisters well?

1438
01:44:37,160 --> 01:44:39,960
The brothel has been busy lately,
so I haven't had a chance to see you properly.

1439
01:44:42,200 --> 01:44:43,080
Is this it?

1440
01:44:43,160 --> 01:44:44,280
No.

1441
01:44:45,080 --> 01:44:47,160
It needs to be thinner than this!

1442
01:44:48,440 --> 01:44:49,560
Bought the wrong one again?

1443
01:44:49,880 --> 01:44:52,200
This is already the thinnest!

1444
01:44:57,800 --> 01:44:58,680
Luo Qian.

1445
01:44:59,720 --> 01:45:00,720
What's wrong?

1446
01:45:01,160 --> 01:45:03,240
Let's change that spring couplet.

1447
01:45:06,680 --> 01:45:09,240
I heard that Master Shenghao came first in the imperial exam.

1448
01:45:10,280 --> 01:45:11,160
Really?

1449
01:45:11,480 --> 01:45:12,120
Mm.

1450
01:45:12,920 --> 01:45:14,520
And he's getting married too.

1451
01:45:15,320 --> 01:45:18,360
They say because Lord Yun Changxian passed away,
he needs to carry on the family line.

1452
01:45:18,920 --> 01:45:20,040
I see...

1453
01:45:23,000 --> 01:45:26,520
It's a relief that he's doing well.

1454
01:45:40,040 --> 01:45:44,040
May disasters melt away like spring snow, and blessings rise like summer clouds.

1455
01:45:44,120 --> 01:45:46,920
It seems our fate ends here, my lord.

1456
01:46:17,000 --> 01:46:20,760
Your face appears in my dreams every night, but now it has become blurry.

1457
01:46:22,520 --> 01:46:24,120
I miss you so much.

1458
01:46:25,640 --> 01:46:27,480
But the harder I try to remember,

1459
01:46:28,760 --> 01:46:30,120
the blurrier it becomes.

1460
01:46:32,360 --> 01:46:33,480
Just once,

1461
01:46:35,240 --> 01:46:36,360
Even if only for a moment,

1462
01:46:37,880 --> 01:46:39,000
I wish I could see him again...

1463
01:46:44,360 --> 01:46:45,480
[Country Woman] Beautiful, truly beautiful.

1464
01:46:45,560 --> 01:46:48,120
Such fine work, yet you charge so little?

1465
01:46:49,160 --> 01:46:51,000
I'm already grateful that you let me paint.

1466
01:46:52,520 --> 01:46:55,080
I heard you're going to help Eun-sook with farm work again today.

1467
01:46:55,160 --> 01:46:57,720
Why have you been working for days on end?

1468
01:46:58,040 --> 01:46:59,880
Because there's someone I want to see.

1469
01:47:01,400 --> 01:47:02,280
I'm planning to visit him.

1470
01:47:03,560 --> 01:47:05,160
[Country Merchant 1] This outfit suits you perfectly.

1471
01:47:07,880 --> 01:47:09,000
By the way, where is the magistrate?

1472
01:47:09,080 --> 01:47:09,960
Has he already left?

1473
01:47:10,280 --> 01:47:11,160
[Country Merchant 2] Not yet.

1474
01:47:11,960 --> 01:47:13,560
[Country Merchant 3] I heard the new magistrate

1475
01:47:13,640 --> 01:47:15,720
is the top scholar who passed the imperial exam.

1476
01:47:17,240 --> 01:47:20,280
Why would a top scholar take a post in a place like this?

1477
01:47:20,360 --> 01:47:21,240
Exactly.

1478
01:47:21,320 --> 01:47:24,600
Isn't this remote area usually for exiled officials?

1479
01:47:24,920 --> 01:47:25,800
No.

1480
01:47:26,120 --> 01:47:28,680
I heard he volunteered to come here.

1481
01:47:28,760 --> 01:47:29,400
Volunteered?

1482
01:47:29,720 --> 01:47:30,360
The new top scholar has arrived!

1483
01:47:39,320 --> 01:47:40,440
Luo Qian.

1484
01:47:40,760 --> 01:47:42,600
The new magistrate wants to see you.

1485
01:47:42,680 --> 01:47:43,560
Me?

1486
01:47:43,640 --> 01:47:45,960
He's looking for a portrait painter.

1487
01:47:46,520 --> 01:47:48,120
He's very satisfied with your work.

1488
01:47:48,440 --> 01:47:51,720
As soon as the magistrate takes office,
he wants a portrait painted?

1489
01:47:52,760 --> 01:47:53,640
Need I say more?

1490
01:47:55,880 --> 01:47:57,000
But you'll still paint it, right?

1491
01:48:00,200 --> 01:48:01,560
Make him pay more silver.

1492
01:48:06,440 --> 01:48:08,760
[Country official] Magistrate,
the painter has arrived.

1493
01:48:25,640 --> 01:48:27,240
My name is Zi Luoqian.

1494
01:48:58,280 --> 01:48:59,880
Are you Zi Luoqian?

1495
01:49:11,240 --> 01:49:12,360
You forgot to take me away.

1496
01:49:13,160 --> 01:49:15,240
Why did you send me away?

1497
01:49:17,480 --> 01:49:18,120
Luoqian,

1498
01:49:18,440 --> 01:49:20,760
I will definitely resolve everything
and come back for you.

1499
01:49:21,080 --> 01:49:21,799
For now...

1500
01:49:21,800 --> 01:49:23,400
Stay here for now.

1501
01:49:29,720 --> 01:49:31,800
I really like

1502
01:49:32,120 --> 01:49:33,480
your painting.

1503
01:49:37,640 --> 01:49:39,480
What are you standing there for?

1504
01:49:39,560 --> 01:49:40,680
Come into my arms quickly.

1505
01:49:41,720 --> 01:49:43,560
Have you forgotten your husband so soon?
